1
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,340
Master,

2
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,640
according to nearby residents,

3
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,200
Qian Yong was spotted here.

4
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:39,039
What exactly did the informant say?

5
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,400
The informant is an old man

6
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,660
who walks his dog after dinner every day.

7
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,479
According to him,

8
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:44,800
this house has been

9
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,120
vacant for twenty years.

10
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,440
But there's been a lot of noise lately,

11
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,640
so he kept an eye on it.

12
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,840
The man he found

13
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,340
has physical features

14
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,400
very similar to the person on the wanted poster.

15
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,729
So he called the police.

16
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,759
We've sent people to search everywhere,

17
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:58,620
but found no trace of the suspect.

18
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,970
Tell everyone to keep looking.

19
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,440
Yes.

20
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,890
Stop tearing them down.

21
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,820
They are all over the city.

22
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,420
Can you tear them all down?

23
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,610
I'm here for you.

24
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,000
Trust me.

25
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,130
Let me update everyone.

26
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,360
Based on the forensic report

27
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,560
and the suspect's confession,

28
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,600
we can basically confirm that

29
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:32,320
the crime process of the July 25 case is now clear.

30
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,250
Look, everyone.

31
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,520
On the murder weapon that killed Tian Liang,

32
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,320
we extracted Brother Kuai's DNA.

33
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,760
According to Brother Kuai's confession,

34
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,960
he was instructed by Ye Qiming that day.

35
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,320
A message was sent

36
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,640
to an unknown number.

37
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,760
After our verification,

38
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,640
this number belongs to Liu Weishan.

39
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,170
However,

40
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,800
Liu Weishan spent the whole day

41
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,960
in the club,

42
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,780
so he couldn't have committed the crime.

43
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,079
This photo

44
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:58,440
was recovered from Lu Yang's phone.

45
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,400
Look at this corner of the photo.

46
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,490
It looks a lot like Liu Weishan.

47
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,200
None of the details of the case

48
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,320
can be linked to Liu Weishan right now.

49
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,200
Only this photo

50
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,860
and this text message.

51
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:12,160
The case is gradually becoming clear.

52
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,220
Yu Na must be working for Liu Weishan.

53
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,360
Once we catch Yu Na,

54
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,690
we should be close to the truth.

55
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,250
But unfortunately,

56
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,930
we can't summon her.

57
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,880
There's indeed not enough evidence to summon her.

58
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,200
We have to leave it at that.

59
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:27,060
But we've been there so many times

60
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,620
and haven't even seen her.

61
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,800
She's definitely hiding something.

62
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,130
So she's hiding from us.

63
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,210
Let's see how long she can hide.

64
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,680
Officer Shen?

65
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,220
This is Xia Lin.

66
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,720
Can you go see Song Qing with me?

67
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,560
Sure.

68
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,680
Did Song Qing ever give you anything?

69
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,100
What kind of thing?

70
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,200
What are you looking for?

71
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,740
Actually, I don't know what it is either.

72
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,880
If Song Qing gave you anything,

73
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,700
I hope you can give it to me.

74
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,560
Why?

75
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,320
Song Qing is dead.

76
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,040
I want this to end quickly,

77
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,440
and I don't want to involve anyone else.

78
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,650
How is it?

79
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,960
Any discoveries?

80
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,480
I kept avoiding this before.

81
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,320
I was afraid to look at anything.

82
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:53,560
But reading the report just now,

83
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,280
I felt like she was

84
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:58,540
actually holding something in her hand.

85
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:05,130
Whatever she was holding tightly before she died

86
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,960
must be a very important clue.

87
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:13,250
I didn't tell you in detail that night.

88
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:15,520
Let me reiterate,

89
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:18,080
you don't have to say it if you don't want to.

90
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,200
Really.

91
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,520
When we first met,

92
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,660
I was investigating a case at her school.

93
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,780
She was a journalism student.

94
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,000
A very brave girl.

95
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:37,040
Stubborn.

96
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,730
She was always doing reckless things.

97
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:44,120
It was pretty scary.

98
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:49,970
When she found out I was investigating at her school,

99
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,280
she insisted on being my informant.

100
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,240
It was too dangerous for her.

101
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,620
I didn't agree.

102
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,360
Partly because I was afraid for her safety,

103
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,780
and partly because

104
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,440
the case was complex and urgent.

105
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,560
That might have been what she was pursuing.

106
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,290
Don't blame yourself too much.

107
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,280
The last time we met,

108
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:19,800
she told me

109
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,440
she found a new lead.

110
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,400
I was young then

111
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,330
and eager to solve the case.

112
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,240
So I just...

113
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,260
I should have stopped her.

114
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,440
Shen Feng.

115
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,080
It wasn't up to you to decide.

116
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,180
Do you understand?

117
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,659
Captain Jiang.

118
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,960
I need a favor.

119
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,240
Xia Lin called me

120
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,560
and said she wanted to see Song Qing.

121
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,640
Can you go with me?

122
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:24,920
I'm sorry.

123
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,160
Song Qing.

124
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,840
I just saw you chatting with Mr. Xia.

125
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:58,700
I didn't go over because I was afraid of disturbing you.

126
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,200
Thank you.

127
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,440
Mr. Xia said...

128
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:09,880
This...

129
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:13,050
This USB drive was left to me by Song Qing before she died.

130
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,200
Give it to Shen Feng.

131
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,040
If Song Qing gave you anything,

132
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,960
I want you to give it to me.

133
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,400
I want this to be over soon.

134
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:42,560
I don't want to involve anyone else.

135
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:48,880
Who let you in?

136
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:52,040
Mr. Xia covered for Ye Qiming, so...

137
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:55,840
Could Song Qing's death

138
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,320
be related to Ye Qiming?

139
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:07,340
It can't be.

140
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,280
It can't be.

141
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,130
What's in this flash drive?

142
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,280
May I ask?

143
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:22,650
Liu Weishan,

144
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,840
Ye Qiming,

145
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,850
and Yu Na.

146
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,720
All of their criminal evidence.

147
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,080
Ye Qiming.

148
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,900
He's involved in this too.

149
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,360
I don't know what role

150
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,810
Ye Qiming plays in this.

151
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,780
But I don't think he killed Song Qing.

152
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,400
It's been so long.

153
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,280
It's time to end this.

154
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:09,620
Five years ago,

155
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:12,000
Tongda Group stood out from the crowd.

156
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:14,240
It was a true dark horse that year.

157
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,240
The content in the video

158
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:17,400
is all evidence of Liu Weishan's crimes.

159
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,840
Due to the severity of the case,

160
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,880
we have reported it to the provincial department.

161
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,800
Now, we will arrest

162
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,760
Liu Weishan and Yu Na.

163
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:31,200
Wang Xianzhi's "Mid-Autumn Festival"

164
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:35,120
is authentically housed in the Palace Museum.

165
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:24,520
Mr. Liu.

166
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,290
We finally meet.

167
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:40,240
I always knew this day would come,

168
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,400
but I didn't expect

169
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:43,840
it to come so soon.

170
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:46,050
From the first day you did all this,

171
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,570
you should have expected this day.

172
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,600
The secret hidden for all these years

173
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,560
has finally been discovered.

174
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,680
After you,

175
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:57,760
Mr. Liu.

176
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:06,850
Chief Wu,

177
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:09,140
this is Liu Weishan's statement.

178
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,880
How did the interrogation go?

179
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,320
The arrest went very smoothly.

180
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,240
After the interrogation,

181
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:15,520
he confessed to his crimes without hesitation.

182
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,450
Based on Liu Weishan's testimony,

183
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,260
the case is basically closed.

184
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,000
So,

185
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:23,760
the case can enter the wrapping-up stage.

186
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:27,040
Arrest Yu Na as soon as possible

187
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:27,840
and put a

188
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,880
perfect end to this case.

189
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:31,920
Yes.

190
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,340
It's finally going to end.

191
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,480
As long as we catch Yu Na,

192
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,200
this case

193
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,760
will be considered closed for now.

194
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:40,160
Yes.

195
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:42,210
How is it?

196
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,640
Being back on the frontline?

197
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,360
Well,

198
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,450
it's been so many years.

199
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,250
It feels very familiar.

200
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,930
But actually, my leaving the frontline back then

201
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,920
wasn't just about Song Qing.

202
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,320
Her incident was definitely the main reason,

203
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,000
but...

204
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,060
if you are on the frontline

205
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:10,680
and always dragging down the people around you because of your own affairs,

206
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:12,340
that feeling is really...

207
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:14,200
pretty bad.

208
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:20,010
But you shouldn't blame yourself.

209
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:23,400
The ones who should be blaming themselves are the criminals.

210
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:24,800
I'm a bit more mature now,

211
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,570
so it's a little better.

212
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,720
In the past, maybe

213
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:31,400
I was just a bit overly sentimental.

214
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:33,920
Shen Feng.

215
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,520
Captain Jiang, what's wrong?

216
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,980
You're hesitating today.

217
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:42,680
No.

218
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,210
I just wanted to ask you,

219
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:49,920
you didn't plan to return to the frontline.

220
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:54,760
These are all personal choices in life.

221
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,640
For instance, me being transferred back this time

222
00:14:57,640 --> 00:15:00,120
is also because in the office, the two of us...

223
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,650
Right, you still remember.

224
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,720
The food is ready.

225
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,840
Have some Xiaodao.

226
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,140
Hello, Captain Jiang.

227
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,280
I have the hostage.

228
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,520
Don't do anything stupid.

229
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:42,320
Where are you?

230
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:43,560
The unfinished building.
